{"tid":2419304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"踎低玩滑板車變「盲點」 　上海6歲女遭七人車輾斃","createTime":"2021-02-23T08:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T06:05:44.000Z","uid":271829,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"be19c67f546f9b5d99c918aa429c425dfc67d551","tid":2419304,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/fYfG9uST6KPwkT9SkMG5TPS4AdA=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NGZHNM46ZFGUJCQGJXCXCXBQLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfYfG9uST6KPwkT9SkMG5TPS4AdA%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNGZHNM46ZFGUJCQGJXCXCXBQLQ.jpg&h=95c9ad30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女童經過汽車旁時剛好蹲著滑板車滑行，結果汽車駕駛沒察覺，直接將她輾斃。翻攝自微博<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n上海有6歲女童疑在街道玩滑板車時，因突然踎跪滑行造成視線盲點，遭一輛私家車輾斃。<br />\n<br />\n事發於周日（21日）上午，鄧姓6歲女童在在母親陪伴下於屋苑內車道玩滑板車，母女相隔數米，期間女童滑行至一個路口時，突然由站姿變為踎跪式滑行，結果數秒後，一輛白色七人車駛出，疑因看不到女童，直接從後方將女童輾壓而過，在女童身後數米的母親，見狀立即衝前拍打汽車後擋風玻璃，但仍未能阻止事故發生，女童當場死亡。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210223/UUGKRDWS3FBG7JQ2OXV5OUUTTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210223%2FUUGKRDWS3FBG7JQ2OXV5OUUTTA%2F&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv35ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=cb290a2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210223%2FUUGKRDWS3FBG7JQ2OXV5OUUTTA%2F&h=03101428\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210223/UUGKRDWS3FBG7JQ2OXV5OUUTTA/</a>"},{"pid":"467b03626b796f79115645908b134484376e5b65","tid":2419304,"uid":378793,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"女嘅冇所謂啦 國家又不需要女人"},{"pid":"f40f66e33f84f2de1c68316b80e28514e451815e","tid":2419304,"uid":362366,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-